{
    "architecture": {
        "system_name": "ABS_Embedded_System",

        "processors": [
            {
                "name": "MainControlUnit",
                "scheduler": "RATE_MONOTONIC_PROTOCOL",
                "clock_period_ms": 1,
                "mips_capacity": 1000,
                "bus_binding": "VehicleBus"
            }
        ],

        "memories": [
            {
                "name": "SystemMemory",
                "size_kb": 8192,
                "bus_binding": "VehicleBus"
            }
        ],

        "buses": [
            {
                "name": "VehicleBus"
            }
        ],

        "devices": [
            {
                "name": "WheelSpeedSensor",
                "category": "sensor",
                "requires_bus_access": true,
                "bus_binding": "VehicleBus",
                "outputs": [
                    {
                        "name": "wheel_speed",
                        "data_type": "Speed"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "name": "BrakePressureActuator",
                "category": "actuator",
                "requires_bus_access": true,
                "bus_binding": "VehicleBus",
                "inputs": [
                    {
                        "name": "brake_pressure_command",
                        "data_type": "Pressure"
                    }
                ]
            }
        ],

        "processes": [
            {
                "name": "ABSControlProcess",
                "processor_binding": "MainControlUnit",
                "memory_binding": "SystemMemory",
                "inputs": [
                    {
                        "name": "wheel_speed_input",
                        "data_type": "Speed"
                    }
                ],
                "outputs": [
                    {
                        "name": "brake_pressure_output",
                        "data_type": "Pressure"
                    }
                ],
                "threads": [
                    {
                        "name": "WheelSpeedMonitorThread",
                        "subprogram": "ReadWheelSpeed",
                        "periodic": true,
                        "period_ms": 10,
                        "deadline_ms": 10,
                        "priority": 3,
                        "inputs": [
                            {
                                "name": "wheel_speed",
                                "data_type": "Speed"
                            }
                        ],
                        "outputs": [
                            {
                                "name": "processed_speed",
                                "data_type": "Speed"
                            }
                        ],
                        "compute_execution_time_ms": 2
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "LockDetectionThread",
                        "subprogram": "DetectLock",
                        "periodic": true,
                        "period_ms": 20,
                        "deadline_ms": 20,
                        "priority": 2,
                        "inputs": [
                            {
                                "name": "processed_speed",
                                "data_type": "Speed"
                            }
                        ],
                        "outputs": [
                            {
                                "name": "lock_detection_result",
                                "data_type": "Boolean"
                            }
                        ],
                        "compute_execution_time_ms": 5
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "BrakePressureControlThread",
                        "subprogram": "AdjustBrakePressure",
                        "periodic": true,
                        "period_ms": 15,
                        "deadline_ms": 15,
                        "priority": 1,
                        "inputs": [
                            {
                                "name": "lock_detection_result",
                                "data_type": "Boolean"
                            }
                        ],
                        "outputs": [
                            {
                                "name": "brake_pressure_command",
                                "data_type": "Pressure"
                            }
                        ],
                        "compute_execution_time_ms": 3
                    }
                ],
                "connections": [
                    {
                        "source": "WheelSpeedMonitorThread.processed_speed",
                        "destination": "LockDetectionThread.processed_speed"
                    },
                    {
                        "source": "LockDetectionThread.lock_detection_result",
                        "destination": "BrakePressureControlThread.lock_detection_result"
                    }
                ],
                "process_port_connections": [
                    {
                        "process_port": "wheel_speed_input",
                        "thread_component": "WheelSpeedMonitorThread",
                        "thread_port": "wheel_speed",
                        "direction": "process_to_thread"
                    },
                    {
                        "process_port": "brake_pressure_output",
                        "thread_component": "BrakePressureControlThread",
                        "thread_port": "brake_pressure_command",
                        "direction": "thread_to_process"
                    }
                ]
            }
        ],

        "subprograms": [
            {
                "name": "ReadWheelSpeed",
                "language": "C",
                "parameters": [
                    {
                        "name": "wheel_speed",
                        "data_type": "Speed",
                        "direction": "in"
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "processed_speed",
                        "data_type": "Speed",
                        "direction": "out"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "name": "DetectLock",
                "language": "C",
                "parameters": [
                    {
                        "name": "processed_speed",
                        "data_type": "Speed",
                        "direction": "in"
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "lock_detection_result",
                        "data_type": "Boolean",
                        "direction": "out"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "name": "AdjustBrakePressure",
                "language": "C",
                "parameters": [
                    {
                        "name": "lock_detection_result",
                        "data_type": "Boolean",
                        "direction": "in"
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "brake_pressure_command",
                        "data_type": "Pressure",
                        "direction": "out"
                    }
                ]
            }
        ],

        "connections": [
            {
                "source": "WheelSpeedSensor.wheel_speed",
                "destination": "ABSControlProcess.wheel_speed_input"
            },
            {
                "source": "ABSControlProcess.brake_pressure_output",
                "destination": "BrakePressureActuator.brake_pressure_command"
            }
        ],

        "system_connections": [
            {
                "source": "MainControlUnit",
                "destination": "VehicleBus",
                "kind": "bus_access"
            },
            {
                "source": "SystemMemory",
                "destination": "VehicleBus",
                "kind": "bus_access"
            },
            {
                "source": "WheelSpeedSensor",
                "destination": "VehicleBus",
                "kind": "bus_access"
            },
            {
                "source": "BrakePressureActuator",
                "destination": "VehicleBus",
                "kind": "bus_access"
            }
        ],

        "flows": [
            {
                "name": "WheelSpeedFlow",
                "kind": "source",
                "source": "WheelSpeedSensor.wheel_speed"
            },
            {
                "name": "BrakePressureFlow",
                "kind": "sink",
                "destination": "BrakePressureActuator.brake_pressure_command"
            },
            {
                "name": "ABSControlFlow",
                "kind": "path",
                "source": "WheelSpeedSensor.wheel_speed",
                "destination": "BrakePressureActuator.brake_pressure_command"
            }
        ],

        "end_to_end_flows": [
            {
                "name": "ABS_EndToEndFlow",
                "flow_sequence": [
                    {
                        "component": "WheelSpeedSensor",
                        "port": "wheel_speed",
                        "flow_type": "source"
                    },
                    {
                        "component": "ABSControlProcess",
                        "port": "wheel_speed_input",
                        "flow_type": "path"
                    },
                    {
                        "component": "WheelSpeedMonitorThread",
                        "port": "wheel_speed",
                        "flow_type": "subprogram"
                    },
                    {
                        "component": "WheelSpeedMonitorThread",
                        "port": "processed_speed",
                        "flow_type": "subprogram"
                    },
                    {
                        "component": "LockDetectionThread",
                        "port": "processed_speed",
                        "flow_type": "subprogram"
                    },
                    {
                        "component": "LockDetectionThread",
                        "port": "lock_detection_result",
                        "flow_type": "subprogram"
                    },
                    {
                        "component": "BrakePressureControlThread",
                        "port": "lock_detection_result",
                        "flow_type": "subprogram"
                    },
                    {
                        "component": "BrakePressureControlThread",
                        "port": "brake_pressure_command",
                        "flow_type": "subprogram"
                    },
                    {
                        "component": "ABSControlProcess",
                        "port": "brake_pressure_output",
                        "flow_type": "path"
                    },
                    {
                        "component": "BrakePressureActuator",
                        "port": "brake_pressure_command",
                        "flow_type": "sink"
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
    },

    "assumptions": [
        "Un seul capteur de vitesse générique est utilisé pour simplifier l'architecture, bien que 4 capteurs soient typiquement nécessaires dans un système ABS réel.",
        "Les périodes des threads ont été choisies pour respecter les contraintes temps réel critiques, mais pourraient être ajustées en fonction de tests supplémentaires.",
        "Les sous-programmes sont implémentés en C pour des raisons de performance et de déterminisme.",
        "Le mécanisme de repli en cas de panne matérielle (ex: défaillance du capteur) n'est pas modélisé en détail mais pourrait être ajouté via un thread de surveillance supplémentaire."
    ],

    "corrections": [
        "Les priorités des threads ont été ajustées pour respecter l'ordre Rate Monotonic (période la plus courte = priorité la plus haute).",
        "Les connexions entre threads ont été explicitement définies pour garantir un flux de données déterministe."
    ],

    "warnings": [
        "La simplification à un seul capteur de vitesse peut ne pas être suffisante pour un système ABS réel, où chaque roue doit être surveillée individuellement.",
        "Les mécanismes de sécurité avancés (ex: désactivation progressive de l'ABS) ne sont pas modélisés en détail et devraient être ajoutés pour une implémentation complète."
    ],

    "impossible_requests": []
}
